profile_positions.description:
Leading PROOF’s strategic work on change communication, reputation management, employee engagement and alignment, helping PROOF's clients in many industries improve their company performance.

As a member of the agency's management team actively involved in the overall management of the agency and the definition of the business strategy.

- Developing lasting relationships with our key clients;
- Building award-winning client cases; 
- Being a major contributor to the growth of the our agency; 
- Playing key roles in internal processes such as recruiting, coaching, talent development; 
- Leading pro-bono projects

Overview of some of the clients I worked for:
Action, COFRA, Dura Vermeer, ING Group, KLM, NN Group, NN Hungary, NN Investment Partners, Randstad, thyssenkrupp, Tata Steel Europe, UMC Utrecht, Upfield
